c: 9
v: 61
t: "No muri bo (indyarya), hari ababuza amahoro umuhanuzi (Muhamadi) bavuga bati \"We yumva ibyo abwiwe byose\". Vuga uti \"Yumva ibyiza kuri mwe, akemera Allah, akemera ibyo abwiwe n’abemera, kandi akaba impuhwe kuri babandi bemeye muri mwe\". Ariko babandi babuza amahoro Intumwa ya Allah, bazahanishwa ibihano bibabaza"